Introduction
2140 001 077 0617, more commonly referred to as Joanne, is a genius who completed groundbreaking research advancing AI and became the youngest CEO of WISDOM at age 24. Working with Roger, the sitting President of America, she is a Traditionalist who designs new technology for the WISDOM system that manages the citizens.

Since she assumed her position at WISDOM, her cunning personality has allowed her to implement more controlling OMs in the lower and middle class. Her modifications have created an almost 24/7 monitoring system across the country.

As CEO of WISDOM she attends council meetings that decide government policy and national defense and system maintenance. She has no political background, but her presence is important because the government controls the WISDOM system through her.

Joanne works closely with Roger, and is often seen together with him outside official government and company business. She is also a childhood friend of Harper and has since reconnected with her after becoming CEO.

Appearance
Joanne is a taller than average woman with tanned skin. Her chestnut hair is often pulled into a log hanging ponytail that reaches her waist in length. Her eyes are rounded and are colored a dull navy hue. Due to her position as a scientist she is often seen in a lab coat or a jacket of similar style. She prefers to only be seen in public wearing business suits or similar masculine formal attire.

Personality
Joanne cultivates a sophisticated and intelligent personality that she treats as her public image. When she is around Roger, she acts diligent and rational to keep her on his good side and make sure that he trusts her. Joanne is deceitful towards him, gaining his trust in the hopes that she will be able to gain his position and status in the future. Roger is oblivious to her goals, which allows her to slowly build up her influence in WISDOM and amongst government officials. Due to her nature, many people avoid her out of self-preservation. Harper is the one close friend she has left that she can feel comfortable and relaxed around.
